<div class="summary__text">
  <header class="summary__header">

    <h3 class="summary__heading"><a  href="/publications/2020/11/keith-mines-future-us-latin-america-policy">Keith Mines on the Future of U.S. Latin America Policy</a></h3>

    
              <p class="meta">
    Thursday, November 12, 2020

</p>
      
              <p class="meta">
  <strong>By:</strong>

  <a href="/people/keith-mines" title="View profile">Keith Mines</a>
</p>
      
      
    

  </header>

              

      <p>Intense polarization in Bolivia, Venezuela, and Colombia will present Washington with significant challenges in the years ahead. But USIP’s Keith Mines says, for the most part, leaders in those countries “are looking for a way forward … there’s a more realistic framework of coexistence that’s emerging.”</p>
  


        
    
              <p class="meta"><strong>Type:</strong> 

      <a href="/publications?publication_type%5B0%5D=11#filters">Podcast</a>  
</p>
      
